  "original_title": "\u0b90.\u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd.\u0b8e\u0baa\u0bcd. \u0b89\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "IMF To the Council of the Covenant",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The United People's Power has demanded that the Staff Level Agreement with the International Monetary Fund be tabled in Parliament next Tuesday.",
        "United People's Shakti Member of Parliament and Chairman of the Public Finance Committee, Kalanithi Harsha de Silva has made this request to President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "Harsha de Silva said during a press conference today (4) that if the President fails to do so, he will use his authority as the Chairman of the Public Finance Committee to reveal the document. (a)"
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Council of the Covenant",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
